window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Unleash the beast!</b>&nbsp;</p> <p>Deep in the heart of Texas, Brawley vows to build a base, explore Red Haven, and protect his women.</p> <p><b>Seven orders. Seven amazing powers. Seven beautiful teachers.</b>&nbsp;</p> <p>He needs to work hard, crack strands, and avoid the attention of those hunting him. And oh yeah, his family and friends want to know why he’s shacking up with five gorgeous women and stockpiling a mountain of ammo. Meanwhile, his newly released Beast just wants to teach all enemies a lesson they’ll never forget....</p> <p><b>Don’t mess with Texas!</b>&nbsp;</p> <p>But how can Brawley succeed when psionic outlaws seize neighboring ranches, threatening to kick off a bloody range war?&nbsp;</p> <p><b>Warning: Like my other work, this series contains explicit scenes. It has violence and a harem element.</b></p>"; 
